1- install node.js
2- npm i --global yarn 
3- at power shell opened as administrator  run command => "Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser"
4- done know yarn is working 


moving to yarn 

To switch from npm to yarn, we need to:
1-Remove the package-lock.json file (if it exists)
2-Install yarn globally (if not already installed)
3-Generate a new yarn.lock file

npm install -g yarn
del package-lock.json
cmd /c del package-lock.json
yarn install
